(18, 1, '2021-05-12 01:35:28', '2021-05-12 01:35:28', '<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>Program 2021</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Sunday 10th January &nbsp;&nbsp;Hawker/Lane/Miles Trio&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>Sunday 24th January &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;SM4  featuring Steve Martin Quartet.<br>Sunday 31st January: &nbsp;Pacific Mainstream Jazz Band.<br>Sunday 14th February: Jez and the Jazz Heads with Jeremy Hawker. &nbsp;<br>Sunday 28 February: Love and starlight.<br>Sunday 14 March: &nbsp;Usual suspects with Larry Thomson<br>Sunay 28 March: &nbsp;RB4<br>Sunday 11th April  Generations of Jazz<br>Sunday 25th April  Anzac Day  Red Poppies Band</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Sunday 9th May (which is a special day when we celebrate all mothers in our lives), &nbsp;the Jazz Club is joining forces with The Fish Inn and taking part in their Mothers Day Buffet celebrations.<br>We are encouraging Jazz Club members to come along and join in the fun on this occasion.<br>The Jazz session will run from 5 to 8 pm-&nbsp;doors open at 4.45 pm. &nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Fish Inn Mothers Day Jazz Buffet. &nbsp;Jazz Buffet (includes jazz ticket) &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Time Period 5pm till 8pm<br>Adults $45.00 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Child 11yrs to 16 yrs $25.00 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Child 2yrs to 10yrs $15.00 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Child under 2 yrs Free</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Tickets must be purchased in advance through Townsville Tickets  please see the link below to the Townsville Tickets site.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Music for the evening will be provided by &nbsp;</strong><strong>&nbsp;D. Russ and Friends</strong><strong>.</strong><strong>&nbsp;Sarah Lane on Vocals &nbsp;<br>Dylan Russell  Guitar &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Jeremy Hawker  Guitar and Bass Pedals &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Nat Gray  Drums</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>The staff at the Fish Inn will be hosting this event and seating will be arranged by them. &nbsp;If you wish to sit in a group with your friends, please book together at the same time if you can.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Alternatively, to advise seating requests, &nbsp;after you purchase your tickets  Phone Julie 0412 408 019 or Coralie 0431 618 618. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Book here:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://townsvilletickets.com.au/event/13095\">https://townsvilletickets.com.au/event/13095</a></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Looking forward to a great celebration on Mothers Day.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Programs', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'programs', '', '', '2021-05-12 05:07:06', '2021-05-12 05:07:06', '', 0, 'https://www.thach.co/jc/?page_id=18', 0, 'page', '', 0),
