 and continued to operate had it not been for many dedicated voluntary committee members who gave their time freely to help manage a successful jazz club. &nbsp;Whilst its not possible to name all committee members club records show the following people have filled the Presidents role since the first AGM in 1995:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1995  1996 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Brian Linforth</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1997 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Len Kingsun</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1998  1999 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Brian Lane</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1999  2003 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Neil Walsh</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2003 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Neil Walsh / Acting President Bob Spillane</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2004  2006 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Bob Spillane</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2007 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Bob Spillane / Acting Presidents Brian Lane &amp; Ken Burnes</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2008  2009 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Ken Burnes</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2010  2015 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&n