(140, 1, '2021-05-16 12:11:24', '2021-05-16 12:11:24', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Come and enjoy our regular jazz nights</strong><strong><br></strong>We feature a range of very talented local bands playing great jazz music in a relaxed yet vibrant environment. The regular jazz nights feature a sit-in bracket and dancers are most welcome.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Meals and bar facility are available.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bookings are required  Phone Coralie Costigan, Club Secretary &nbsp;&nbsp;0431 618 618<br>Where: The Fish Inn on The Strand (near the Rockpool)</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;2nd&nbsp;and 4th&nbsp;Sunday 5pm till 8 pm</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Check the Program page for dates</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cost: &nbsp;Cover charge for regular club nights</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$10 members, $15 non members. &nbsp;Eftpos available. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":56,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https://www.thach.co/jc/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/homepageimage1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-56\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Next:<strong>&nbsp;9 May &nbsp;D. Russ and Friends.&nbsp;Sarah Lane on Vocals &nbsp;<br>Dylan Russell  Guitar &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Jeremy Hawker  Guitar and Bass Pedals &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Nat Gray  Drums</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>To avoid disappointment book early. &nbsp;Every previous session has 